OL,7,Fdetention suspended for two years at
OL,8,FBirmingham Crown Court on Thursday,
OL,9,FMay 16.
OL,11,FBoth twins, who are on Universal
OL,12,FCredit, were ordered to carry out 175
OL,13,Fhours of unpaid work and 40 days
OL,14,Frehabilitation activity.
OL,16,FMark Joyce was told to pay #750
OL,17,Fcompensation and Jason was instructed
OL,18,Fto pay #1,500.
