OL,6,FThe family made attempts to reassure
OL,7,Fthe twins they did not 'want any
OL,8,Ftrouble' but then Jason punched one
OL,9,Fman in the face in an unprovoked
OL,10,Fattack.
OL,12,FThe victim's father tried to get Jason
OL,13,Foff his son resulting in a melee
OL,14,Funfolding.
OL,16,FMark Joyce tried swinging a pool cue
OL,17,Fwhile Jason exited the immediate area
OL,18,Fonly to return wielding a machete.
OL,20,F"It's almost a miracle no-one was hurt
OL,21,Fby the blade," Mr Phillips said.
