OL,13,Fas they left, the court was told.
OL,15,FAs the footage of the incident was
OL,16,Fplayed noises could be heard coming
OL,17,Ffrom defendants' family in public
OL,18,Fgallery prompting Judge Bond to issue
OL,19,Fthem a warning.
